album.name: Veritas Diaboli Manet in Aeternum: Chaining the Katechon

wiki.summary: 'Veritas Diaboli Manet in Aeternum: Chaining the Katechon' is a 22-minute EP containing a single song, recorded by the French black metal band Deathspell Omega. Chaining the Katechon was released through Norma Evangelium Diaboli on December 8, 2008. Veritas Diaboli Manet in Aeternum translates to 'The Truth of the Devil Remains in Eternity').
